Class BinarySearchTree.TreeIterator

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    BinarySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>

    public class BinarySearchTree.TreeIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<E>
    Iterator class for looping through the elements in order or in reverse order.

    The remove() method is unsupported.
